@startuml
title LeadelMarche - Diagramme de communication (process de vente complet)

skinparam dpi 300
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam nodesep 40
top to bottom direction
scale max 2200 width

object "Caissier/Caisse rapide" as User
object "POSView" as View
object "POSController" as Ctrl
object "SalesService" as Sales
object "CustomerService" as Cust
object "InventoryService" as Stock
object "PromotionService" as Promo
object "FastCheckoutService" as Fast
object "SaleRepository" as SaleRepo
object "ReceiptService" as Receipt
object "ReceiptRepository" as ReceiptRepo
object "Printer/EmailGateway" as Out

' Grille de placement (stable et compacte)
User -[hidden]down- View
View -[hidden]down- Ctrl
Ctrl -[hidden]right- Sales
Sales -[hidden]right- Cust
Cust -[hidden]right- Stock
Stock -[hidden]right- Promo
Promo -[hidden]right- Fast
Sales -[hidden]down- SaleRepo
SaleRepo -[hidden]right- Receipt
Receipt -[hidden]right- ReceiptRepo
ReceiptRepo -[hidden]right- Out

User -> View : 1 start
View -> Ctrl : 2 commandeUI
Ctrl -> Sales : 3 gererPanier
Sales -> Cust : 4 identifierClient
Sales -> Stock : 5 reserverStock
Sales -> Promo : 6 calculerPromos
Ctrl -> Fast : 7 controleRapide
Sales -> SaleRepo : 8 saveVente
Sales -> Stock : 9 decrementerStock
Sales -> Receipt : 10 genererTicket
Receipt -> ReceiptRepo : 11 saveTicket
Receipt -> Out : 12 printOrEmail
Sales -> Ctrl : 13 retourResultat
Ctrl -> View : 14 afficherResultat
View -> User : 15 ticketClient

note right of Fast
Legende detaillee:
1-2  : demarrage vente (badge + point de vente)
3    : ajout/modification panier
4    : client carte fidelite ou Anonyme
5-6  : stock + promotions (immediate/cagnotte)
7    : caisse rapide (poids + appel aide)
8-12 : finalisation + ticket
13-15: confirmation de vente
end note

note bottom
Le diagramme reste un diagramme de communication UML:
objets + messages numerotes.
Le detail est reporte dans la legende pour eviter la superposition.
end note

@enduml
